  <addon id="4490">
  <name>X-notifier (for Gmail,Hotmail,Yahoo,AOL ...)</name>
  <type id="1">estensioni</type>
  <guid>{37fa1426-b82d-11db-8314-0800200c9a66}</guid>
  <slug>xnotifier</slug>
  <version>3.1.3</version>
  <status id="4">Revisione completa effettuata</status>
  <authors>
        <author id="104093">
      <name>Byungwook Kang</name>
      <link>https://addons.mozilla.org/it/thunderbird/user/tobwithu/?src=api</link>
    </author>      </authors>
  <summary>Notifier for gmail, yahoo, hotmail, aol and more webmails.
X-notifier(aka WebMail Notifier) checks your webmail accounts and notifies the number of unread emails...
Supports : gmail, yahoo, hotmail, POP3/IMAP, facebook, twitter and more</summary>
  <description>X-notifier(aka WebMail Notifier) checks your webmail accounts and notifies the number of unread emails.
You can use multiple accounts in a same host.

Currently supports
 - Gmail (Gmail &amp;amp; Google Apps)
 - Yahoo (&lt;a href=&#34;http://outgoing.mozilla.org/v1/c30e788b5bc87010971185b66aec0f7d2ef9fc0aa04209a6e3d7eb7a8c782754/http%3A//yahoo.com&#34; rel=&#34;nofollow&#34;&gt;yahoo.com&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;http://outgoing.mozilla.org/v1/e671e2d985c29f60bbe11c05318b72f546c5784d0c552df1f8e46dfcd70a3659/http%3A//ymail.com&#34; rel=&#34;nofollow&#34;&gt;ymail.com&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;http://outgoing.mozilla.org/v1/86ba081094d45ef4ddb0c6dd46e9bde188215e76512a07087325694aecde52b5/http%3A//rocketmail.com&#34; rel=&#34;nofollow&#34;&gt;rocketmail.com&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;http://outgoing.mozilla.org/v1/bf6835ed9018b76a44122f8e5496b6b24b38ccbf26e45648b9cd83132551b508/http%3A//yahoo.co.jp&#34; rel=&#34;nofollow&#34;&gt;yahoo.co.jp&lt;/a&gt;)
 - Hotmail (&lt;a href=&#34;http://outgoing.mozilla.org/v1/15692169aeffbb13145025891d2d14272fc405e63e6ecf8bdbe144f1fe8021f3/http%3A//hotmail.com&#34; rel=&#34;nofollow&#34;&gt;hotmail.com&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;http://outgoing.mozilla.org/v1/b08fb7c152062bd8732740b61319985ff4136e9a4a935ad249b61538cf641b27/http%3A//msn.com&#34; rel=&#34;nofollow&#34;&gt;msn.com&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;http://outgoing.mozilla.org/v1/dbfc13b09923ffee137ec82e00b48d2e59b80ce7c8e06e38f0ea23ebd7bb70b1/http%3A//live.com&#34; rel=&#34;nofollow&#34;&gt;live.com&lt;/a&gt;)
 - AOL (&lt;a href=&#34;http://outgoing.mozilla.org/v1/edff2ac240d89c8b774da11c809c838447e78a3a38ebec9133c7a500fee16cd5/http%3A//aol.com&#34; rel=&#34;nofollow&#34;&gt;aol.com&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;http://outgoing.mozilla.org/v1/fc14062ae4d4624a73cc51098dd1d4e8717ef0e012fcbce88ffc8d656c770486/http%3A//aim.com&#34; rel=&#34;nofollow&#34;&gt;aim.com&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;http://outgoing.mozilla.org/v1/6b59bf8b94224a366968d483216df0e725c9c203992ca62f2fd4a4f66ebeeb53/http%3A//mail.com&#34; rel=&#34;nofollow&#34;&gt;mail.com&lt;/a&gt;)
 - Daum (&lt;a href=&#34;http://outgoing.mozilla.org/v1/73586d10ae2d8d4e428fba8b42418ee53ec1a718db150121eab8d3533fb6741a/http%3A//daum.net&#34; rel=&#34;nofollow&#34;&gt;daum.net&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;http://outgoing.mozilla.org/v1/5396d4c149ed7cf25437bad9d4bcf3530777ca590ad418927931858d22f42eb1/http%3A//hanmail.net&#34; rel=&#34;nofollow&#34;&gt;hanmail.net&lt;/a&gt;)
 - Naver
 - Nate (&lt;a href=&#34;http://outgoing.mozilla.org/v1/589827927a513149b8efd8f626be1890a5dea973553954146c83d3f8066ee7f2/http%3A//nate.com&#34; rel=&#34;nofollow&#34;&gt;nate.com&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;http://outgoing.mozilla.org/v1/48778d584f37a240859a240fc00c82ceb091fc87bfda30bb06218a14d642a842/http%3A//empas.com&#34; rel=&#34;nofollow&#34;&gt;empas.com&lt;/a&gt;)
 - POP3/IMAP

Below sites are supported by user script.
 - Facebook
 - AdSense
 - Twitter
 - LinkedIn
 - &lt;a href=&#34;http://outgoing.mozilla.org/v1/8e90ef2e665f065ba5ce5cd2136bc335af9b76ac6bf947f79b97dafa6d941ea2/http%3A//sina.com&#34; rel=&#34;nofollow&#34;&gt;sina.com&lt;/a&gt;
 - &lt;a href=&#34;http://outgoing.mozilla.org/v1/e53f8d53f1f0714f6c8ee399b64721c2e64536fa1f588908771e6f8958cdcc66/http%3A//yandex.ru&#34; rel=&#34;nofollow&#34;&gt;yandex.ru&lt;/a&gt;
 - &lt;a href=&#34;http://outgoing.mozilla.org/v1/e9472a22c41474fa0457bff3adf953dcb92a4082dc902fb400f1c8f8d607238d/http%3A//163.com&#34; rel=&#34;nofollow&#34;&gt;163.com&lt;/a&gt;(&lt;a href=&#34;http://outgoing.mozilla.org/v1/a30c876502bb7d8e7105c522497d49bf641cba6823f71aee786abbf9c4e55980/http%3A//126.com&#34; rel=&#34;nofollow&#34;&gt;126.com&lt;/a&gt;, &lt;a href=&#34;http://outgoing.mozilla.org/v1/9182c60a1caa8af906426c42f97f92556a3d191eccea6918d2b135d56434f870/http%3A//yeah.net&#34; rel=&#34;nofollow&#34;&gt;yeah.net&lt;/a&gt;)
 - &lt;a href=&#34;http://outgoing.mozilla.org/v1/f174e397acedd250ff8d7e8df23b2d1776b75f88c8c74c88f6c3c85903dc6315/http%3A//mail.ru&#34; rel=&#34;nofollow&#34;&gt;mail.ru&lt;/a&gt;
 - &lt;a href=&#34;http://outgoing.mozilla.org/v1/2761252591a61e7239c66c190499c11f4721eff221191d13fa68705ed7558c9d/http%3A//www.gmx.net&#34; rel=&#34;nofollow&#34;&gt;www.gmx.net&lt;/a&gt;
 - &lt;a href=&#34;http://outgoing.mozilla.org/v1/b5e039d25f0babbc2953a283da15adcc81c350d02acd6beba17eeae4e8eb8058/http%3A//www.gmx.com&#34; rel=&#34;nofollow&#34;&gt;www.gmx.com&lt;/a&gt;
 - &lt;a href=&#34;http://outgoing.mozilla.org/v1/03ac595b91a1e30fa72dae5eaf554b0b7d619f35e4d6cc38a422ee4a40046c9d/http%3A//freemail.web.de&#34; rel=&#34;nofollow&#34;&gt;freemail.web.de&lt;/a&gt;
 - &lt;a href=&#34;http://outgoing.mozilla.org/v1/fa129c995ad6f1eaee728593015f28cc3e4bacf97b99a54d7fc4d6af63dca03a/http%3A//poczta.fm&#34; rel=&#34;nofollow&#34;&gt;poczta.fm&lt;/a&gt;(&lt;a href=&#34;http://outgoing.mozilla.org/v1/cc647434b9b64d382f1b83a39778d3a284081e8ebb750d717a7e54432f874d8e/http%3A//poczta.interia.pl&#34; rel=&#34;nofollow&#34;&gt;poczta.interia.pl&lt;/a&gt;)
 - &lt;a href=&#34;http://outgoing.mozilla.org/v1/016cac7a1ca07bfaec374859680ddfdcff70fb96e477dafa624452f2ca2879e8/http%3A//www.qq.com&#34; rel=&#34;nofollow&#34;&gt;www.qq.com&lt;/a&gt;
 ......

&lt;a href=&#34;http://outgoing.mozilla.org/v1/d319bfb89aca2483f54d62e21a404e448b6d090b9fbb6a7c95787f5388870402/http%3A//xnotifier.tobwithu.com/scripts.php&#34; rel=&#34;nofollow&#34;&gt;You can find more scripts for X-notifier 3 here.&lt;/a&gt;
