    </author>      </authors>
  <summary>Mailbox Alert allows you to specify, for each seperate mail folder, a message, sound and/or a system command that will be executed when new mail is found there. ...</summary>
  <description>Mailbox Alert allows you to specify, for each seperate mail folder, a message, sound and/or a system command that will be executed when new mail is found there. 

This way, you specify different actions for less important folders, or no action at all.</description><license>
